1
00:00:03,301 --> 00:00:04,930
What are they doing?
他们在干什么

2
00:00:05,140 --> 00:00:07,861
Nothing. Just lying there.
什么也没干  只是趴着

3
00:00:08,010 --> 00:00:10,720
Maybe it takes a while for something to happen.
可能得等一会儿才会有情况出现

4
00:00:14,334 --> 00:00:16,756
A very long while, by the looks of it.
他们盯着看了好一阵

5
00:00:17,070 --> 00:00:19,018
Let's get a little closer.
咱们再靠近一些吧

6
00:00:19,730 --> 00:00:22,741
Not too close, now. Remember what Bernie...
别太近了  还记得伯尼说

7
00:00:23,767 --> 00:00:25,389
What was that?
什么声音

8
00:00:25,716 --> 00:00:27,272
OOOOONNAAAA!
乌娜

9
00:00:27,470 --> 00:00:29,134
What is it, Silky?
怎么了 西尔奇

10
00:00:29,236 --> 00:00:31,723
I think I just squashed a crab!
我好像压碎了一只螃蟹

11
00:00:32,792 --> 00:00:36,276
Ooooh noooooo! I... I can't look.
糟糕  我  我不敢看

12
00:00:36,630 --> 00:00:41,352
It's okay, Silky. Crabs are able to grow a new shell, remember?
没事的 西尔奇  螃蟹能长出新壳  记得吗

13
00:00:41,550 --> 00:00:45,186
We shouldn't have come too near! Bernie was right!
我们不应该靠这么近的  伯尼说得对

